data.description: Location - Location - Location!!! Only a half-mile from the front gate of Dollywood!! This charming 2BR/2BA proven money-maker cabin sits on its own full half-acre lot and has all the convenience, privacy, and charm any renter could hope for. It has a seasonal mountain view. The cabin produced $57,000 in income in 2021, and $47,000 in 2022 before management fee deductions. Owner bought and furnished this brand new cabin in 2020. Everything is practically brand new! Gas log fireplace inside and a fire-pit with chairs out back surrounded by a string of outdoor LED lighting for ambience creates the perfect mountain getaway experience. Add in the hot tub on the back porch and the star-lit tree in back at night make for a wonderful family experience. Vacations come and go, but memories last a lifetime! Being sold fully furnished and stocked, this cabin is ready to begin making money the day you close. Current rental management requests new owners allow a 90 day curing period during which reservations already booked will be honored. All rental revenues transfer to new owners immediately upon closing. All information obtained through owner and courthouse records, and while assumed accurate should be verified by buyers. All inspections and survey if needed are recommended.  Interior Photos Coming Soon!
